Definition: a public statement containing information about an event that has happened or is going to happen
Example: the announcement appeared in the local newspaper; the promulgation was written in English
Synonyms: verb, communication, announce, promulgation, promulgate, statement, a, public, containing, information, about, an, event, that, has, happened, or, is, going, to, happen, the, appeared, in, local, newspaper, was, written, English
Category: noun.communication
